121
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,040
Don’t listen to him.

122
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,320
I wouldn’t dare deceive you.

123
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,180
Wouldn’t dare?

124
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,480
Didn’t you take

125
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,000
half of the silver the other day?

126
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,440
Get down.

127
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,920
Fraud.

128
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,800
That's too much.

129
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,440
Cheating.

130
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,080
Indeed.

131
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:19,360
Leave, fraud.

132
