147
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:15,320
Does this have anything to do with the 80,000 taels of silver?

148
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:16,440
It’s none of your business.

149
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,900
Do you know someone or not?

150
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,840
I don’t.

151
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,200
Useless.

152
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:37,610
Young Madam.

153
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:40,120
