165
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:03,010
We’ll be busy in the days ahead.

166
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,120
Okay.

167
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,320
Manager Liu.

168
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:17,320
Yes?

169
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:20,720
It seems your tavern is doing quite well.

170
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,120
Thanks to your support.

171
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:24,920
Over the years, with the care from you and your father,

172
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,780
I've been able to open a few branches in the capital.

173
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,080
I’ve heard

174
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,120
that the new wine brewed by the Fourth Young Madam

175
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:35,280
of the Marquis' Mansion is quite popular recently.

176
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:40,840
