177
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:43,760
Her wine is indeed excellent.

178
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:46,360
Many wealthy customers have been asking about it

179
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,600
and want to taste it.

180
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,560
However, you instructed us last time,

181
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:50,220
so I dare not

182
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,560
sell it.

183
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:54,120
I see that you are a wise man, Manager Liu.

184
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:54,960
Yes.

185
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:58,040
Whether that particular wine is sold or not doesn’t matter much.

186
00:08:58,040 --> 00:09:00,960
But whether you want to continue doing business with the Li family

187
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:03,880
depends on whether you understand the rules.

188
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:06,740
Second Young Madam. Don't worry.

189
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,960
None of the taverns or shops under my name

190
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,240
will sell her wine.

191
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,560
It's not just that you can't sell it.

192
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:15,000
No shop in the entire capital

193
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,360
will sell her wine.

194
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,540
Our Li family has enough influence for that.

195
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,320
But don’t worry.

196
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,360
I will speak well of you

197
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,240
in front of my father.

198
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,770
Thank you, Second Young Madam.

199
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:28,600
