Take care, Second Young Madam.

201
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:35,680
Young man.

202
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,600
Please, do me a favor

203
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,680
and take the wine.

204
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,640
Sorry, bro.

205
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:39,760
We really can't

206
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:40,960
sell this wine here.

207
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:41,480
You should try elsewhere.

208
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,680
Qin, what's going on?

209
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,120
Fourth Young Madam.

210
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:44,960
All the taverns and shops

211
