222
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:06,120
Sorry.

223
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,040
but we don’t sell that wine here.

224
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,720
Fourth Young Madam.

225
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,840
What should we do?

226
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,210
Our wine is priced high.

227
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,650
If we sell it ourselves,

228
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,960
we won't be able to sell it.

229
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,840
Even the Vice Director Huang from the Board of Astronomy couldn’t buy this wine.

230
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,700
