233
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,600
The man who just walked past was him.

234
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,800
Do you know where we can find him?

235
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,800
He’s on duty at the Board of Astronomy outside the city, in the bamboo forest.

236
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:33,560
Thank you.

237
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,920
Qin.

238
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:36,040
Take the wine back to the liquor workshop.

239
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:37,120
